Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.70,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}對著無法起飛的螺旋槳做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.90,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝著天空的另一半抬頭望去 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.01,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光著腳丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.45,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:23.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}無論誤會與否 就是對生活充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:36.89,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的寶物 藏起來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:45.49,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也無法發現那顆深藏起來的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.49,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕嚕咕嚕轉上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.60,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:57.63,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:01.34,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢想一定會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:12.87,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們要永遠在一起哦
